---
title: Chermoula-Spiced Honey Lamb Rump with Sesame Roast Root Veggie Toss & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Our lamb rump is taken to the next level when rubbed with our chermoula spice and honey concoction. With a bountiful
sesame-laced roast veggie toss, you can induldge in this meal whilst knowing that it is light on the carbs.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
